    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Ongoing Platform Support</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Support the infrastructure that makes wish-granting possible. Help us maintain 
          the platform, connect practitioners with projects, and grow the ecosystem.
        </p>
